Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:28.00,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}小鹿乱撞  坐立不安  要去哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:30.76,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}一想到车到山前必有路  就抬起头向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:33.93,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}一定能做到呢  只要和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.93,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}能做到？  还是不能？  能做到！  那来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:40.31,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}自身一人的力量很小？  才不！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.35,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}都是慢慢积攒起来的呢  只要不放弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:46.02,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}虽说努力不一定会有成果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.94,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不过也会有一点点好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.69,0:01:49.28,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:52.36,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}世界很和平呢  去附近人家串门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:55.45,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}一点点地把朋友圈扩大起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:58.16,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}每天的问候很重要的说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:01.20,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}看起来又有精气神了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:01.50,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:07.09,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不管是什么人  在我的面前  跟人争吵什么的我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:09.96,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}要好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.30,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}好啦快来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:13.05,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}要开开心心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.22,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}好啦快来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:19.01,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}虽然兴趣爱好八竿子打不着  还是很合拍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:16.76,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}兴趣不同？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:22.39,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}所以说不要随随便便的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:22.98,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}求你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:25.52,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不要随随便便度过今天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:25.90,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}不要这样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:31.15,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}还不着急到明天呢  一起来好好地玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:31.48,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}请多指教咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:34.61,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}所以说不要随随便便的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.11,OPCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2\an1}这可不行哦
